docs {
  # Slack Connection Status
  
  Check if an Inkeep user has connected their Slack account.
  
  **Auth:** Session token (from "1. Sign In" in manage/)
  
  **Endpoint:** `GET /work-apps/slack/users/status`
  
  **Required Query Params:**
  - `userId` - Inkeep user ID to check
  
  **Returns:**
  - `connected: true/false`
  - `connection` - Object with connection details if connected:
    - `connectionId` - Link record ID
    - `slackUserId` - Slack user ID
    - `slackTeamId` - Slack team ID
    - `slackDisplayName` - Slack username
    - `linkedAt` - Link timestamp
}
